content: In the ninth move of the game, White captured, with his piece at 25, two opponent pieces (on squares 20 and 09) and reached square 03. The annotation for this move would be: 9. 25 x 3.
translations: ita:Nella nona mossa della partita, il Bianco ha catturato, con il suo pezzo a 25, due pezzi avversari (sui quadretti 20 e 0
